trans-unit.source: Represents an entry in either back or forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma entrada no back ou do histórico de navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] implements a navigation history service that stores one entry for each piece of content that has been previously navigated to, just like navigation history in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)]implementa um serviço de histórico de navegação que armazena uma entrada de cada peça de conteúdo que foi anteriormente navegou, tal como o histórico de navegação no [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Navigation history comprises two stacks, one that remembers back navigation history, and one that remembers forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: Histórico de navegação compreende duas pilhas, aquele que memorizou histórico de navegação de back- e aquele que memorizou histórico de navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: An entry for the current item is added to back navigation history when a forward navigation occurs.
trans-unit.target: Uma entrada para o item atual é adicionada ao fazer uma cópia de histórico de navegação quando ocorre uma navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: This occurs in the following situations: - The `Navigate` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Isto ocorre nas seguintes situações: - `Navigate` método é denominado (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.Navigate%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The `GoForward` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: -O `GoForward` método é denominado (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoForward%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The forward button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -O botão reencaminhar no painel de navegação [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] que é apresentado do navegador atual ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Likewise, an entry for the current item is added to forward navigation history before a back navigation occurs, which happens when: - The `GoBack` method is called (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).
trans-unit.target: Da mesma forma, uma entrada para o item atual é adicionada ao histórico de navegação de avanço antes de uma navegação back ocorre, o que acontece quando: - `GoBack` método é denominado (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.GoBack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: - The back button on the navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that is displayed from the current navigator ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).
trans-unit.target: -O botão anterior no painel de navegação [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] que é apresentado do navegador atual ([!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: Each entry in back and forward navigation history is an instance of the JournalEntry class.
trans-unit.target: Cada entrada em volta e o histórico de navegação de avanço são uma instância da classe JournalEntry.

trans-unit.source: Each JournalEntry object encapsulates information about a particular navigation, including a name for the entry (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), whether the entry is kept alive (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) and the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] for the content that is navigated to (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).
trans-unit.target: Cada objeto JournalEntry contém informações sobre uma navegação específica, incluindo um nome para a entrada (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>), se a entrada é mantida activa (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A>) e o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)] para o conteúdo que é utilizado (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A>).</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Source%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.KeepAlive%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntry.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects in back navigation history by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Pode obter todos os objetos JournalEntry no histórico de navegação de back-através da enumeração de <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>ou <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Propriedades.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For forward navigation history, you can retrieve all the JournalEntry objects by enumerating the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties.
trans-unit.target: Para o histórico de navegação de avanço, pode obter todos os objetos de JournalEntry por enumerar o <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>ou <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Propriedades.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If you need to remove the most recent JournalEntry object from back navigation history, to prevent navigation to it, for example, you can call the `RemoveBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), which removes the JournalEntry object and returns a reference to it.
trans-unit.target: Se precisar de remover o objeto de JournalEntry mais recente do histórico de navegação anterior, para impedir a navegação, por exemplo, pode chamar o `RemoveBackEntry` método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>), que remove o objeto de JournalEntry e devolve uma referência ao mesmo.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.RemoveBackEntry%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You cannot add JournalEntry objects to navigation history, however, because you can neither instantiate nor derive from JournalEntry, and because no type implements a member to do so.
trans-unit.target: Não é possível adicionar objetos JournalEntry ao histórico de navegação, no entanto, uma vez que pode instanciar nem derivar JournalEntry e porque nenhum tipo implementa um membro para o fazer.

trans-unit.source: However, you can add custom <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> objects to back navigation history by calling the `AddBackEntry` method (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> object to an internally-created JournalEntry object, which is then added to the back navigation history.
trans-unit.target: No entanto, pode adicionar objetos <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>personalizados para fazer uma cópia de histórico de navegação ao chamar o `AddBackEntry` método (<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A>); <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService>adiciona o <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>objeto a um objeto de JournalEntry criou internamente, que, em seguida, é adicionado ao histórico de navegação back.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationService.AddBackEntry%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.CustomContentState>
